<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Yoga Center</title>
    <style>
                /* Reset default browser styles */
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        /* Set global styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            background-image: url('https://unsplash.com/photos/n7a2OJDSZns');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
        }
        
        /* Style navigation menu */
        nav {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            padding: 10px;
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            z-index: 999;
        }
        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
        }
        nav li {
            margin-right: 20px;
        }
        nav a {
            color: #333;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        /* Style header section */
        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 0;
        }
        header h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        header p {
            font-size: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        /* Style main content section */
        main {
            padding: 50px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        }
        main h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        main ul {
            list-style: none;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        main li {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        main p {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
            </style>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/signin">Sign In</a></li>
            <li><a href="/register">Register</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to our Yoga Center!</h1>
        <p>Our center is dedicated to helping individuals improve their physical, mental and emotional well-being through the practice of yoga. We offer a wide range of classes suitable for all levels, from beginners to advanced practitioners.</p>
    </header>
    <main>
        <h2>Our Classes:</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Hatha Yoga</li>
            <li>Vinyasa Yoga</li>
            <li>Restorative Yoga</li>
            <li>Yin Yoga</li>
            <li>Kundalini Yoga</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We also offer private sessions and workshops to deepen your practice and enhance your understanding of yoga.</p>
        <p>Our experienced teachers are passionate about sharing the benefits of yoga and creating a welcoming and supportive community. Whether you're looking to improve your flexibility, reduce stress, or simply take some time for yourself, we have a class that can help you achieve your goals.</p>
        <p>Join us on the mat and discover the transformative power of yoga.</p>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
